    "metaTitle": "Summer Vacation Deals for Families: Make Memories for Less | VacationDeals.to",
    "metaDescription": "summer vacation deals families — real prices, honest reviews, and proven tactics to save 70-88% on resort stays. Updated for 2026.",
    "category": "interests",
