    "slug": "how-to-negotiate-timeshare-exit",
    "title": "How to Exit a Timeshare Without Getting Scammed",
    "metaTitle": "How to Exit a Timeshare Without Getting Scammed | VacationDeals.to",
    "metaDescription": "exit timeshare without scam — real prices, honest reviews, and proven tactics to save 70-88% on resort stays. Updated for 2026.",
    "category": "interests",
    "publishDate": "2026-04-16",
