    "slug": "how-to-maximize-resort-amenities",
    "title": "How to Maximize Resort Amenities You're Already Paying For",
    "metaTitle": "How to Maximize Resort Amenities You're Already Paying For | VacationDeals.to",
    "metaDescription": "maximize resort amenities — real prices, honest reviews, and proven tactics to save 70-88% on resort stays. Updated for 2026.",
    "category": "interests",
