    "slug": "8-best-beachfront-vacation-deals",
    "title": "8 Best Beachfront Vacation Deals (Sand Between Your Toes)",
    "metaTitle": "8 Best Beachfront Vacation Deals (Sand Between Your Toes) | VacationDeals.to",
    "metaDescription": "best beachfront vacation deals — real prices, honest reviews, and proven tactics to save 70-88% on resort stays. Updated for 2026.",
    "category": "destinations",
    "publishDate": "2026-04-16",
